{"tid":2368414,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳搭上千億社長約飲酒　橋本環奈事業隨時玩完","createTime":"2021-01-16T07:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T18:59:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8987483988b0399f5e300b430823f42cdbbfc6c7","tid":2368414,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"日本當紅女星橋本環奈，出道以來憑可愛臉孔與健康形象走紅，成為藝能界搶手貨。下月便滿22歲的她，近日卻爆出緋聞，被指與大型娛樂事業公司USEN的有米社長宇野康秀關係親密。出名愛飲酒的她，經常與年長36歲的宇野相約到東京西麻布的私竇酒吧摸酒杯底。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210115/photo/bkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg?20210115175628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20210115175628&h=72b59db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210115/photo/bkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_03p.jpg?20210115175628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20210115175628&h=f390f891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n橋本曾與去年合演電影《輝夜姬想讓人告白》的尊尼男團King &amp; Prince主將平野紫耀傳緋聞，但有指平野只是煙幕。57歲的宇野身家豐厚，高達1000億日圓(約74.5億港元)。橋本於2019年加盟對方出資的事務所，又為他經營的影視串流服務U-NEXT擔任代言人，外界擔心橋本會步女星剛力彩芽後塵，剛力搭上富商前澤友作後形象拜金，令演藝事業玩完。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210115/photo/bkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_04p.jpg?20210115175628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210115165559356-0115_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20210115175628&h=c288cfe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73a63c46be6d89d4f7ae166bf70efdc9949bd4fa","tid":2368414,"uid":80047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"ae930fd6e8342ce3fc02842d04f46e7c72b3c3fa","tid":2368414,"uid":220309,"li